# API Configuration
# In production, use HTTPS endpoint to ensure secure communication
# Example for production: VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com/api
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080/api

# Security Notes:
# - The API client enforces HTTPS when the frontend is served over HTTPS
# - Passwords are only sent during login over the configured API URL
# - All subsequent requests use JWT token-based authentication
# - Never store or log passwords in the frontend
